CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,FThe government will launch a "people's
OL,7,Fpanel" to allow the public to have
OL,8,Ftheir say over Labour's controversial
OL,9,Fplans to introduce digital IDs.
OL,11,FThe move confirms the government's
OL,12,Fplan to push ahead with digital IDs,
OL,13,Fwhich they say will create a system of
OL,14,F"government by app", despite concerns,
OL,15,Fincluding among Labour MPs.
OL,17,FCritics of digital ID have previously
OL,18,Fraised fears over individual privacy
OL,19,Fand concerns that an app would
OL,20,Fsideline older and more vulnerable
OL,21,Fmembers of society.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,FWhile the detail has not yet been
OL,7,Fannounced, it is thought that digital
OL,8,FID cards would be a form of ID,
OL,9,Fprovided free of charge to those
OL,10,Fentitled to live or work in the UK.
OL,11,FThey would be stored on smartphones
OL,12,Fand act as official proof of identity.
OL,14,FThe consultation - which ministers are
OL,15,Fcalling a "people's panel" - will
OL,16,Fbring together a diverse range of
OL,17,Fpeople from across the UK, allowing
OL,18,Fthe public to "have their say" about
OL,19,Fhow any digital ID scheme should work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,FParticipants are set to be asked to
OL,7,Fconsider how much information should
OL,8,Fbe included on a digital ID, and what
OL,9,Fgovernment services it could
OL,10,Fcollaborate with.
OL,12,FThis could include services such as
OL,13,Fgetting a driving license or checking
OL,14,Ftax codes.
OL,16,FThe consultation will also explore age
OL,17,Flimits around digital ID, after
OL,18,Fministers indicated children as young
OL,19,Fas 13 could be included in the rollout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,FLaunching the scheme, the Chief
OL,7,FSecretary to the Prime Minister Darren
OL,8,FJones warned that public services need
OL,9,Fto "catch up" with those offered by
OL,10,Fthe private sector.
OL,12,FHe pointed to online banking as an
OL,13,Fexample of where the private sector is
OL,14,Fleaving state services behind in terms
OL,15,Fof delivering a "better customer
OL,16,Fexperience and value for money".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,FOfficials said the prototype of the
OL,7,Fscheme would show how a wider system
OL,8,Fof "government by app" would work,
OL,9,Fwith ambitions to make the set-up as
OL,10,Feasy and secure as online banking.
OL,12,FSeparately, the Cabinet Office
OL,13,Fconfirmed that anyone starting a new
OL,14,Fjob will be required to undergo new
OL,15,Fdigital right-to-work checks by the
OL,16,Fend of the current parliament.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
