OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,FThey added that people "will be able"
OL,7,Fto use the new digital proof of
OL,8,Fidentity for these checks, but they
OL,9,Fcould also choose to use other
OL,10,Fdocuments, such as a passport or eVisa
OL,11,Fif they prefer.
OL,13,FThe government had previously said
OL,14,Fthey would introduce mandatory checks
OL,15,Fof the new forms of digital ID, as
OL,16,Fpart of a crackdown on illegal working
OL,17,Fand immigration, but u-turned on that
OL,18,Fdecision earlier this year.
OL,26,@nD@XOUnD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,FITV News reported previously that the
OL,7,Fdecision was taken in early January,
OL,8,Fafter Keir Starmer judged the argument
OL,9,Fover ID cards was too much of a
OL,10,Fdistraction from his new focus on
OL,11,Fbearing down on the cost of living.
OL,13,FSpeaking today on the consultation and
OL,14,Fwider reforms, Jones said his reforms
OL,15,Fwill allow people to "log on and prove
OL,16,Fwho you are to access public services
OL,17,Fmore quickly, easily and securely".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
