OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,F"People too often dread their
OL,7,Finteractions with public services.
OL,8,FEndless telephone calls, complicated
OL,9,Fprinted forms and having to tell your
OL,10,Fstory multiple times to different
OL,11,Fparts of government.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
