OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773169065
OL,3,CGovernment to push ahead with digital
OL,4,CIDs as public to be asked to have say
OL,6,F"I want to change that and make public
OL,7,Fservices work for you. The new digital
OL,8,FID will make that possible, allowing
OL,9,Fyou to log on and prove who you are to
OL,10,Faccess public services more quickly,
OL,11,Feasily and securely.
OL,13,F"Supermarkets, banks and shops have
OL,14,Fall chosen to move their services
OL,15,Fonline because it delivers a better
OL,16,Fcustomer experience and value for
OL,17,Fmoney, and other countries like
OL,18,FEstonia fully digitised public
OL,19,Fservices years ago. We need to catch
OL,20,Fup."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
